Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `ExampleScenario.process` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `ExampleScenario.process` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `ExampleScenario.process` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Element `ExampleScenario.process` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `ExampleScenario.process`, but has no comparisons.
Note available implied context: `ExampleScenario.process.step.process` because `ExampleScenario.process.step.process` is defined as a content reference to `ExampleScenario.process`."/>
